President Muhammadu Buhari is in a meeting with some Northern Governors in the Presidential Villa, Abuja. Chief of Staff to the President, Prof Ibrahim Gambari, is also in the meeting. The Governors were led by chairman of Northern Governors Forum, Simon Lalong. Others in the delegation are Governors Atiku Bagudu (Kebbi); Nasir El-Rufai (Kaduna); Mai Mala Buni(Yobe); Abubakar Bello(Niger) and Abdullahi Sule (Nasarawa). Details shortlyâ€¦